54
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,840
And Chen Yanyun,

55
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,080
to show the Gu family respect,

56
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,240
even invited the wife

57
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,639
