58
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,360
You're lying.

59
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:52,800
I don't believe you.

60
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:54,840
You must be lying.

61
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,919
