What...
What's going on?

67
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,120
Quick, go inform Mrs. Feng.

68
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:28,639
Yes.

69
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:53,160
I'm not even afraid of Lord Chen.

70
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,639
