71
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:57,279
Greetings, Uncle.

72
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,759
Nice to meet you.

73
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,639
As my elder,

74
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:03,000
