110
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,800
And don't let a word of this get out.

111
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:49,879
Got it.

112
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:52,680
I'd better go myself.

113
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:54,680
