144
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,399
Do you

145
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,120
have feelings for Xian?

146
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,160
I've always

147
00:08:17,759 --> 00:08:18,920
