164
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,519
Because I love him.

165
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,960
I was going to tell you tomorrow.

166
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,200
I didn't expect you

167
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,399
