174
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,159
Young Lord,

175
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,799
what brings you here today?

176
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:15,240
- Why not go to the...
- Shut up!

177
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,039
