249
00:15:07,759 --> 00:15:10,240
I'll leave you and Yanyun to it.

250
00:15:10,799 --> 00:15:12,000
Please excuse me.

251
00:15:14,559 --> 00:15:15,159
Zhang Fang,

252
00:15:15,399 --> 00:15:16,799
